  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Easy Park Plus系统画一个状态图，核心是要表现停车场从空到满，再到维护模式的完整生命周期。起点应该是初始状态，然后进入EmptyLot。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "EmptyLot"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，EmptyLot就是无车状态。那车辆进入后应该转移到什么状态？是直接进入Full，还是中间有个过渡？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmptyLot",
        "Full"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "必须有中间状态，叫PartiallyFull。车辆停入时，EmptyLot转到PartiallyFull，继续停才到Full。反过来，取车时Full也能退回PartiallyFull，PartiallyFull可以回到EmptyLot。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmptyLot",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Full",
        "Park vehicle",
        "Remove vehicle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把这三个状态画好了，标注了EmptyLot是'No vehicles parked'，PartiallyFull是'Some slots occupied'，Full是'All slots occupied'。转换条件也都标了Park vehicle和Remove vehicle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmptyLot",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Full"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有一个关键场景：维护模式。任何状态都可能需要进入Maintenance，比如设备检修。触发条件是'Enter maintenance mode'。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Maintenance",
        "Enter maintenance mode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，EmptyLot、PartiallyFull、Full这三个状态都能转到Maintenance，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmptyLot",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Full",
        "Maintenance"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对。而且维护结束后有两种恢复方式：一种是'Reset lot'，直接清空回到EmptyLot；另一种是'Restore previous state'，回到维护前的PartiallyFull状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Maintenance",
        "EmptyLot",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Reset lot",
        "Restore previous state"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
